Skeem Saam actor Patrick Seleka, who plays the character of Katlego Peterson, will be the host of a new cooking show on Netflix. Seleka took to social media to share the exciting news of making his dream of four years come true. As the host of The Cook Along he will venture across South Africa eating and replicating dishes prepared by celeb chefs using farm-fresh ingredients. “A township kid with a passion for food goes on a quest to learn more about food. Turning my Skeem Saam storyline into a reality. This is the making of the aspiring chef SLK,” he wrote.   For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.